Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 09:24:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Dark/Light/System theme toggle to FleetFlow header

- CSS variable token system for light/dark themes
- 3-way toggle in header beside role badge, before Logout
- Hardcoded dark background/text colors swept to CSS variables
- Theme persists in localStorage, respects prefers-color-scheme
- No Firebase, job, money, receipt, or crew logic touched

https://claude.ai/code/session_01KucBQZHAdsRE3Qh1oJvuz3
---
 index.html | 128 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
 1 file changed, 121 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

diff --git a/index.html b/index.html
index 46b7871..1a709a3 100644
--- a/index.html
+++ b/index.html
@@ -95,23 +95,87 @@ Timestamp:             2026-04-13T02:37:42Z
 <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.8.0/firebase-firestore-compat.js"></script>
